### Crear una nueva jugada
POST http://localhost:8090/api/v1/jugadas HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "usuarioId": 1,
    "moveSan": "e4",
    "moveUciFrom": "e2",
    "moveUciTo": "e4",
    "fen": "rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1",
    "pgn": "1. e4"
}

###

### Crear otra jugada
POST http://localhost:8090/api/v1/jugadas HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "usuarioId": 1,
    "moveSan": "Nf3",
    "moveUciFrom": "g1",
    "moveUciTo": "f3",
    "fen": "rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/4P3/8/PPPP1PPP/RNBQKBNR b KQkq e3 0 1",
    "pgn": "1. e4 e5 2. Nf3"
}

###

### Crear jugada para otro usuario
POST http://localhost:8090/api/v1/jugadas HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "usuarioId": 2,
    "moveSan": "d4",
    "moveUciFrom": "d2",
    "moveUciTo": "d4",
    "fen": "rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1",
    "pgn": "1. d4"
}

